Classification: Reality
Genre: Action | Family | Romance/Dating | Travel
Status: Returning Series
Network: NBC ( USA)

"Love in the Wild" is a new reality show that puts the relationships that people have to the test if it is strong enough. The show puts 10 single men and women in the same place together and all are going to go on the adventure of a lifetime when they are put into deep into the jungle of Costa Rica to find the one and only love for them. This show takes dating the the extreme when there is no house to reside in and they have to find love on their own.
